	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sęvit adhuc pestis apud nos, optime pater <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingere</persName>, ita ut nudiustertius in hoc parvo oppido perierint 20. Hucusque intra spatium trium mensium obiere circiter 400, et nondum finis; habes ergo, cur commendes nos precibus ecclesię tuę.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Huc accedit, quod per decretum gubernatoris <placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolani</placeName> non licet amplius frumenta ex ducatu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolanensi</placeName> ad nos exportari; metuunt enim annonę penuriam propter hasce toto fere mense maio continentes pluvias.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ita fit, ut pestem incipiat subsequi fames, modo non et bellum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolani</placeName> enim colligitur miles et equitatur adversus quos, dominus nostri misereatur, ...</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego cum familia singulari beneficio dei valeo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale et tu cum omnibus fratribus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutat vos vester <persName type="auto_name">Friderychu</persName><note type="misc">dieser Satz von anderer Hand.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l93" cert="high">Clavenna</placeName> prima iunii 1564.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4037" cert="high">Zanchus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">H[enrico] Bullingero</persName>, ecclesię <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinę</placeName> pastori fidelissimo et patri optimo.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurum</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
